080-tbmc.nlpi.edu.tw.eproxy.nlpi.edu.tw:2048/cnnewsapp/servlet/ShowService?&path=ftimg/&title=/cn1960/03/22/00001.pdf|journal=《中央日報》|issue=|doi=|others=|year=1960-03-22|volume=|page=|pmid=}} {{Registration required}}</ref>
